{"tid":1744541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港即將出現黑名單","createTime":"2019-11-21T19:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T20:27:09.000Z","uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b532840128e223933cc25f4daacce48f9df5293d","tid":1744541,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:33:51.000Z","msg":"香港即將出現黑名單<br />\n<br />\n黑名單 (臺灣)<br />\n<br />\n黑名單一般指駐外單位不予核發簽證的參考名&shy;單，或者對於出境者不再核准其入境的政策，被視為打壓異己、維護專制統治、以及宣稱維護國家安全的重要手段。<br />\n<br />\n在台灣，黑名單特別指國民黨政府來臺之後，在國民黨專制的戒嚴時期，針對主張臺獨、民主或同情左派以及共產主義等政治異議人士，採取不予核發簽證或禁止入境措施。針對「黑名單」返臺的禁令在1992年解嚴之後終止，官方稱「列註人員名單」。台灣解嚴回歸真正的法治社會後才有「不受歡迎人士」名單取而代之。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%91%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE_(%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE_%28%25E8%2587%25BA%25E7%2581%25A3&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt88emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=e259862b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%91%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE_(%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3</a>)<br />\n<br />\n凡是參加過抗爭的香港人，一旦離境就無法回港，入境即逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n「自由．飛」紀錄片 feat.雙城記<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xe6Yrmb1Eqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fxe6Yrmb1Eqw&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt88emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=b52573b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xe6Yrmb1Eqw</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jDpTFNx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjDpTFNx.jpg&h=600c1052&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9e950770a6cab26896700957785a3939bd03373","tid":1744541,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:34:51.000Z","msg":"咁咪整返張黑名單比美國睇囉"},{"pid":"d31aa852f5c81ba080fc5d02117e404d92fdffcc","tid":1744541,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e950770a6cab26896700957785a3939bd03373","tid":1744541,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:34:51.000Z","msg":"咁咪整返張黑名單比美國睇囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:36:53.000Z","msg":"美國是台灣的長期盟友，但是美國當時並沒有幫助台灣的流亡人士"},{"pid":"f136133d562bfdffd86a8ad8902b37eac0948d7e","tid":1744541,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:38:06.000Z","msg":"已經有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但未fc<br />\n<br />\n原來香港一早學支共限制香港人出境<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1744292</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c9d66496bdc0c85ccd7d90ed3fffa8630e2cdf0","tid":1744541,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f136133d562bfdffd86a8ad8902b37eac0948d7e","tid":1744541,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:38:06.000Z","msg":"已經有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但未fc<br />\n<br />\n原來香港一早學支共限制香港人出境<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1744292</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:41:31.000Z","msg":"看到這新聞，想到當年台灣黑名單是被國民黨全球通緝<br />\n<br />\n現在，香港黑名單應該已經被共產黨全球通緝"},{"pid":"aca3bd4c01bcaa294dbe9af5906f404018afb965","tid":1744541,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T19:54:37.000Z","msg":"《臺灣省戒嚴令》，正式名稱為《臺灣省政府、臺灣省警備總司令部布告戒字第壹號》，是由時任中華民國臺灣省政府主席兼臺灣省警備總司令陳誠於1949年5月19日頒布的戒嚴令，宣告自同年5月20日零時（中原標準時間）起在臺灣省全境實施戒嚴，至1987年由時任總統蔣經國宣布同年7月15日解除該戒嚴令為止，共持續38年56天。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E7%9C%81%E6%88%92%E5%9A%B4%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2587%25BA%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%259C%2581%25E6%2588%2592%25E5%259A%25B4%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt88emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=ecbfdd29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E7%9C%81%E6%88%92%E5%9A%B4%E4%BB%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n香港出現黑名單，表示戒嚴已開始"},{"pid":"9b2be4e86646639e82cce2d039cf9cfb1ddb0d6e","tid":1744541,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T20:27:09.000Z","msg":"如果你不相信任何人，任何人也不會相信你"}]}